orm=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Mete.\">Mete.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">360b3</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὁτὲ μὲν . . , ἢ</foreign>. . <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg034.perseus-grc1:1448a:21\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Po.\">Po.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1448a21</biblScope> </bibl> (s. v.l.): also reversely, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἄλλοτε μὲν . . , ὁτὲ δὲ</foreign>. . <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:11:568\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">11.568</biblScope> </bibl>; also <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὁτὲ δέ</foreign> in the second clause, without any correlative in the first, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:17:178\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">17.178</biblScope> </bibl>; <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ S.\">S.</a></author> </bibl> joins <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἔσθ᾽ ὅτε . . , ὅτ᾽ ἄλλοτ᾽ ἄλλον</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg003.perseus-grc1:56\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Aj.\">Aj.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">56</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὁτὲ δέ</foreign> alone, at the beginning of a clause, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0032.tlg014.perseus-grc1:5:8\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ X.\">X.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Cyn.\">Cyn.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.8</bib